{"tid":2029991,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港啲師奶女人咁鐘意揀生果？","createTime":"2020-05-22T13:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T14:00:14.000Z","uid":212509,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27479cfef66e5fda9844aed2108801da58702d78","tid":2029991,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"呢排難搵工，去咗x哥間超級市場做水果部上貨員<br />\n我明白大家購物都想買最好既產品<br />\n但香港班師奶真係唔講得笑<br />\n對蔬果質素既要求分分鐘拍得住古代皇帝揀後宮佳麗<br />\n又要大又要靚又要新<br />\n都算<br />\n最過癮就係佢地視蔬果如黃金<br />\n次次一日開箱水果拎出黎<br />\n成班好似餓狗搶屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圍住個水果籃係咁搶<br />\n好似前世未食果生果咁"},{"pid":"f1247dd9e6d9d754073c9582ee3dd18368504d78","tid":2029991,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"請大家將524 行動正名為反國安法大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029954</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a84027aa9aea19e35aead3782757726d2590d4cb","tid":2029991,"uid":153722,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"你到依家出黎做野，都仲唔明點解師奶（媽媽們）要咁樣揀法咁樣慳錢？"},{"pid":"e8b4f2cc2f4e7d776cdae55d3833ab2f6b9dc2c6","tid":2029991,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:39:53.000Z","msg":"就好似班師奶都唔明點解會有人做上貨員一樣"},{"pid":"46453d07f99912ba0a2a6bf43ab51cb7b6df2ed2","tid":2029991,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"仲要隻隻橙鍊過曬驗屍咁驗"},{"pid":"bf6f060914ddf58357abd672c923d8ae52a1a7b8","tid":2029991,"uid":217411,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"有咩問題，咁生果真係要揀得靚先好味"},{"pid":"41f13340f47e35a5ece1f302d3010d34a6b546c2","tid":2029991,"uid":266336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"正常，就好似買電子產品咁都會查依查路<br />\n<br />\n只不過大家領域上不同，（開箱